# GenAI: Falcon-7B + LangChain (Nursery Rhyme Demo)

This project runs the **Falcon-7B-Instruct** LLM locally using **Hugging Face Transformers** + **LangChain**.
It generates a short nursery rhyme explaining **Artificial Intelligence**.

## Demo Output
Example prompt:
> Explain what is Artificial Intelligence as Nursery Rhymes

## Requirements
- Python 3.10–3.12 recommended
- NVIDIA GPU (optional but faster)
- CUDA installed if you want GPU acceleration

## Installation

```bash
python -m venv .venv
# Windows (PowerShell)
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

pip install -r requirements.txt